                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ZYcat/">B cat</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-10-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">我觉得这本书看一遍远远不够</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
